title: AHS: Apocalypse Episode 10 Breakdown and Details You Missed!
author: Think Story
comment: Wanted to give a HUGE SHOUT OUT to everyone who has followed my videos over the last few months and the tremendous love and support for my growing channel. Daddy loves you very much! 💖💖💖
It’s basically like we watched a whole season just for nothing to really happen. I wanted to see a real showdown between Mallory and Michael. Kind of disappointing 🤷🏾‍♀️
So much for the whole "Mallory is an angel" theory.
I only wish that the final battle would have been a badass magical one.
This season had way to much potential they dropped the ball
